Prince Edward carried on with a public engagement after her fall, but her mother pulled out on an event in Manchester to be by her daughter's side.

Earlier this year it was revealed that Louise, a bridesmaid at Prince William's wedding, had undergone surgery to correct a severe squint caused by exotropia which she had suffered from since birth.

The photographs of the little girl on her morning hack appeared to suggest that the operation had been a success.

